#: admin/partials/reorder-post-within-categories-settings-display.php:40
msgid "A sub-menu is now placed under each post type menu in your dashboard to access the sorting page."
msgstr "Un sous-menu apparaît désormais dans votre tableau de bord, en dessous de chaque type de publication. Il vous permet d’accéder à la page de tri."

#: admin/partials/reorder-post-within-categories-admin-display.php:133
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Oui"

#: admin/partials/reorder-post-within-categories-admin-display.php:138
msgid "No"
msgstr "Non"

